author: PostmodernJukebox
description:
“Heroes” by David Bowie cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Sara Niemietz.
Get The Song: http://www.pmjlive.com/heroes | Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ
World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com | PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

New Year, New PMJ Video! One of our highlights of 2025 was headlining London’s famed Royal Albert Hall, where longtime PMJ collaborator Sara Niemietz performed our version of David Bowie’s “Heroes” (originally recorded with Nicole Atkins in 2016) in front of a packed house of fellow Old Souls.  Here’s a live-in-studio version with Sara to start the year - wishing you all a heroic 2026 (and s/o to anyone that learned about this great Bowie song via the "Stranger Things" finale last night!)

Watch our first cover of this song starring Nicole Atkins: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=foDOGeRFsCY
